>oxygen sensor and an air/fuel mixture gauge. I'd especially like to know 
>whether during light acceleration/cruise whether a (very) lean condition is 
>normal. I have my AFM tuned to be a little on the rich side most of the 
>time, but under certain conditions light throttle/cruise the gauge displays 
>lean. I don't know whether this is normal, a problem, or an exhaust leak 
